APP STORE CONNECT — "App Review Information" хэсэг (Notes for Reviewer)
================================================================================

LOCATION USAGE EXPLANATION:

Maximus Delivery is a last-mile delivery management app used by delivery drivers
to receive, track, and complete delivery orders from warehouse to customer.

SPECIFIC LOCATION FEATURES:

1. MANDATORY STARTUP LOCATION CHECK
   - When: App launches
   - What: GPS location is requested before the app loads
   - Why: The entire app depends on location for route optimization and distance
           calculations — without it, drivers cannot sort or navigate deliveries

2. ROUTE OPTIMIZATION
   - When: Driver taps "Маршрут оновчлох" (Optimize Route) on a delivery package
   - What: Current GPS coordinates sent to server to sort orders by nearest distance
   - Why: Minimizes total travel distance, improving delivery efficiency

3. DELIVERY ORDER DISTANCE DISPLAY
   - When: Package delivery screen loads
   - What: Distance (in km) to each customer address calculated from current position
   - Why: Driver can prioritize nearest deliveries first

4. DELIVERY CONFIRMATION GPS STAMP
   - When: Driver marks order as "Хүргэгдсэн" (Delivered)
   - What: GPS coordinates captured and submitted with delivery confirmation
   - Why: Provides verifiable proof that the driver was at the correct location

5. PARTNER / ROUTE SCREENS
   - When: Partners "All" and "Route" tabs load
   - What: Current location used to calculate proximity to partner locations
   - Why: Helps drivers navigate to the correct partner pickup points

CAMERA USAGE EXPLANATION:

1. DELIVERY PROOF PHOTO
   - When: Driver confirms delivery completion (order detail screen)
   - What: Camera launched to capture a photo as delivery proof
   - Why: Photo is submitted to the server as evidence of successful delivery
   - Access: Only when driver explicitly taps the camera button

CRITICAL PRIVACY NOTES:
- NO BACKGROUND LOCATION TRACKING
- Location is accessed ONLY when user actively uses delivery features
- We use "When In Use" permission only (not "Always")
- Location data is submitted to company server for delivery verification only
- Camera is accessed ONLY when driver intentionally taps the photo button
- Photos are uploaded as delivery proof and NOT stored locally

