================================================================================
NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription (Info.plist)
================================================================================

Maximus Delivery requires your location to optimize delivery routes and verify
order completion. Your GPS position is used to sort delivery addresses by
nearest distance, and is recorded when you confirm a delivery as proof that
you were at the correct location. Location is ONLY accessed while the app is
in use and is NEVER tracked in the background.

================================================================================
NSCameraUsageDescription (Info.plist)
================================================================================

Maximus Delivery uses your camera to capture delivery proof photos. When you
complete a delivery, you can take a photo as evidence of successful handoff.
The photo is uploaded to the delivery record and is NOT stored on your device.

